function Set-ADTShortcut
{
    <#
    .SYNOPSIS
        Modifies a .lnk or .url type shortcut.

    .DESCRIPTION
        Modifies a shortcut - .lnk or .url file, with configurable options. Only specify the parameters that you want to change.

    .PARAMETER LiteralPath
